text: Pelecanimimus (meaning "pelican mimic") is a primitive theropod dinosaur from Spain. It is notable for possessing more teeth than any other member of the Ornithomimosauria (or any other theropod), most of which were toothless.Beaked theropod has most teeth of any theropod - 1994. == References == Category:Theropods Category:Cretaceous dinosaurs Category:Feathered dinosaurs
title: Pelecanimimus
